{
  "stem": "24171.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It was in the middle of the-- not far away from where-- from the gate.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, there was a long one, a long barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it had, in the middle, kind of like a chimney.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We always asked, what for that thing, if they make fire in there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there was never fire in it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So we went there, and sometimes-- Yeah, there was another thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We wound up in another barrack before we went to Guben.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "First of all, in the same barrack, the [INAUDIBLE], that means that-- what she took care on-- on the barrack-- when, you know, in the [INAUDIBLE], and kept on announcing that if there's girls 14 or younger, they should all come and stay out, not be in the-- in the [INAUDIBLE], the, you know, the bed.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And well, we knew, already, that time approximately, that-- what happens to young people, because in-- in Plaszow, they were-- we saw a bunch of children.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the Germans dressed them up like little German things.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There was about 10 of them, something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they were marching in exactly the way that [INAUDIBLE] was, with them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they were going out there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we afterwards, we asked somebody-- because we-- we saw them a few times, and then all of a sudden they're not there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So I asked one of those older people-- which are not older people, but they were before us, there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And she said, you know where they are.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were kind of ready, a little bit, with knowledge that what-- what's going on.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] there was another thing, before, when we came to Auschwitz the second time.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were staying outside, naked-- outside, and we were very thirsty.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
